OL,3,C'Major upgrade' to Met Office system
OL,4,Ccould help avoid flight delays
OL,6,FA "major" upgrade to the Met Office's
OL,7,Fforecasting system could help avoid
OL,8,Fflight delays, the forecaster has said.
OL,10,FIts new system brings clearer and more
OL,11,Faccurate cloud and fog predictions
OL,12,Fneeded for managing flight schedules.
OL,14,FWinter temperature forecasts are also
OL,15,Fcloser to real life, which the Met
OL,16,FOffice said will assist those making
OL,17,Fplans to manage the energy grid, grit
OL,18,Froads and de-ice aeroplanes.
