OL,3,C'Major upgrade' to Met Office system
OL,4,Ccould help avoid flight delays
OL,6,FSevere weather event warnings also can
OL,7,Fbe made sooner as it has extended its
OL,8,Fglobal forecasts from seven to 10 days.
OL,10,FThe forecasters said it is the "most
OL,11,Fsignificant scientific upgrade in more
OL,12,Fthan three years".
OL,14,FScience Minister Lord Vallance said in
OL,15,Fa statement: "The Met Office's new
OL,16,Fsupercomputer has allowed more
OL,17,Faccurate forecasting, particularly for
OL,18,Fcloud and fog, two difficult areas for
OL,19,Fforecasting.
