OL,3,C'Major upgrade' to Met Office system
OL,4,Ccould help avoid flight delays
OL,6,F"We're getting much more realistic
OL,7,Frainfall intensities from the
OL,8,Fmodelling system."
OL,10,FThis follows the forecasters'
OL,11,Fannouncement that it has rained every
OL,12,Fday so far this year in the south west
OL,13,Fof England and South Wales, with 50%
OL,14,Fmore rainfall than usual in January.
OL,16,FMr Vosper added: "The representation
OL,17,Fof cloud in the modelling system has
OL,18,Fimproved, and particularly the height
OL,19,Fof the cloud cover, be it low or high
OL,20,Fcloud and very low cloud which is of
OL,21,Fcourse mist or fog.
