OL,3,C'Major upgrade' to Met Office system
OL,4,Ccould help avoid flight delays
OL,6,F"That greater accuracy is particularly
OL,7,Fbeneficial for aviation.
OL,9,F"When you're trying to (run) busy
OL,10,Fairports, organise flight itineraries
OL,11,Fand run busy airports like Heathrow,
OL,12,Flow cloud and fog can be a real
OL,13,Fproblem, so having more accurate
OL,14,Fforecasts there is very, very
OL,15,Fbeneficial."
OL,17,FIt is the first upgrade on the Met
OL,18,FOffice's supercomputer, supplied by
OL,19,FMicrosoft, that it transitioned to in
OL,20,FMay.
