OL,3,C'Major upgrade' to Met Office system
OL,4,Ccould help avoid flight delays
OL,6,FThe Met Office said: "The upgrade
OL,7,Fmarks a major step forward in the UK's
OL,8,Fweather and climate science capability
OL,9,Fdelivering tangible improvements that
OL,10,Fwill make forecasts easier to
OL,11,Finterpret. "
OL,13,FOn its improved cloud and fog
OL,14,Fguidance, it said: "This advancement
OL,15,Fwill be vital for industries such as
OL,16,Faviation, where precise weather
OL,17,Finformation is critical to manage
OL,18,Fflight schedules, avoid delays, and
OL,19,Fensure safe take offs and landings,
OL,20,Fespecially in situations with low
OL,21,Fcloud bases, mist and fog."
